# DockerHub deployment information
# 
# To push to DockerHub, follow these steps:
#
# 1. Tag your image:
#    docker tag car_price_prediction:latest YOUR_DOCKERHUB_USERNAME/car_price_prediction:latest
#
# 2. Login to DockerHub:
#    docker login
#
# 3. Push the image:
#    docker push YOUR_DOCKERHUB_USERNAME/car_price_prediction:latest
#
# 4. Pull and run from any machine:
#    docker run -p 8000:8000 YOUR_DOCKERHUB_USERNAME/car_price_prediction:latest
